{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For me, all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was for the fall of-- of '41.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had also-- this is another angle-- decided, as I told you, when I came back from Europe, that I was going to do something about this Hitler business.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had read US history, and I became painfully aware that the US has a very bad history, or habit, of not preparing in advance for a war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when the war comes, boom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody gets drafted and cannon fodder gets thrown onto the battlefield with minimum or no training, and they get slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that the best way to avoid that-- as a, as a possible slaughteree, you see-- was to get some advanced training.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not only would I be more effective on the battlefield, but I would have a better chance of survival.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I determined to get into the service of my choice before the war began.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I applied for a commission in the United States Navy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] a week after I got the acceptance from Wisconsin, the Navy said-- sent me that they accepted me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said, we are ordering you to active duty on the 20th of June, 1941.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wrote Wisconsin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, can I postpone my fellowship?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you can reapply.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I wrote the Navy and I called-- I wrote them I guess-- and said, can I-- can I postpone my entrance into the Navy?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can resign your commission, in which case, we can assure you, you will be drafted at once.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And your decision was?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] My decision was obvious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, that was the end of my academic studies for eight years-- seven years.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
